snippet.title: Dunk Dunk | Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Dunk Dunk shoots into the Playtonic Friends lineup!

https://store.steampowered.com/app/2410590/Dunk_Dunk/

Dunk Dunk is a chaotic basketball party game to play alone or in frantic 1v1 or 2v2 matches with friends. Familiar platforming controls make it easy to pick up while stretchy arm controls make mastering the block all important! Dunk across the universe in a variety of locations and customise your Dunker to style on your friends! (or soon to be enemies)

Swish-list now to stay tuned on development and help the game get discovered by more folks!

https://x.com/dunkdunkgame
https://x.com/PlaytonicGames
